<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10494433>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Pseudoscalibregma paraparisp.nov. Holotype (UERJ 9169) representation(A).Anteriorbody withfirst chaetigerous segments in ventral view; (B). Lyrate chaeta; (C). Spinous chaeta; (D). Section of mid-body parapodium, anterior view; (E). Section of posterior body parapodium, anterior view; (F). Section of posteriormost parapodium, anterior view.Abbreviations: dC = dorsal cirrus; Hor = prostomial horn; iP = interramal papilla; Pe = peristomium; Pr = prostomium; vC = ventral cirrus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10494433/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10494435>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Pseudoscalibregma parapari sp. nov., Holotype (UERJ 9169) under light microscopy. (A). Anterior body with first chaetigerous segments, dorsal view; (B). Anterior body with first chaetigerous segments, ventral view; (C). Mid-body, ventrolateral view, stained with Shirlastain A; (D). Lyrate chaetae; (E). Midbody dorsal cirrus in detail, stained with Shirlastain A. (F). Posterior body dorsal cirrus in detail, stained with Shirlastain A; (G). Section of midbody parapodium, anterior view; (H). Lateral view of posterior body, stained with Shirlastain A; (I). Posterior end, ventral view.Abbreviations: Ch1 = chaetiger 1; Ch2 = chaetiger 2; dC = dorsal cirrus; iP = interramal papilla; Nel = neuropodial lobe; Nol = notopodial lobe; Pe = peristomium; PgM = pygidial margin; Pr = prostomium; vC = ventral cirrus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10494435/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10494437>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Pseudoscalibregma parapari sp. nov. (UERJ 9213), sacrificed specimen under SEM. (A). Anterior body, ventral view; (B). Spinous chaetae in detail; (C). Final body, dorsal view.Abbreviations: dC = dorsal cirrus; Hor = horn; Pg = pygidium; Sc = Spinous chaeta." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10494437/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

